Title: [ANN][ENK] Enkronos - Trusted Blockchain Credit System for Data Driven Campaign
Body: Enkronos Apps are built on a highly modular concept, where removing, adjust, scaling or improving any aspect is simple and clean. This removes any authentication or data authorization issues that an application could have and eases the use of all applications throughout the world of Enkronos Apps.
